==English==
===Noun===
'''octavo'''
# a sheet of paper 7 to 10 [[inch]]es high and 4.5 to 6 inches wide, the size varying with the large original sheet used to create it. Made by folding the original sheet three times to produce eight leaves.
# a [[book]] [[page]] the size of such leaves.
# a book of octavo pages

